==Examples==
*''[[Huorn]] = "''Tall tree''"''
*[[Hûr]] = "Fiery spirit"
*''[[Húrin]]''
==Other versions of the legendarium==
In [[Noldorin]] it is meaning "[[dog]]"; the plural is ''hui''.{{references}}
